  <div class="html-fig_description">
    <b>Figure 3.</b>
      UML activity diagram for patient data flow in privacy-preserving healthcare AI. Each step shows how a single patient record is collected, pre-processed, encrypted, and subsequently used for federated model training. The final compliance and auditing phase ensures that privacy regulations are continuously met. Feedback loops allow for risk re-assessment and adaptive cryptographic settings.
