            <div id="main-share-modal" class="reveal-modal reveal-modal-new reveal-modal-new--small" data-reveal aria-labelledby="modalTitle" aria-hidden="true" role="dialog">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="small-12 columns">
                <h2 style="margin: 0;">Share Link</h2>
            </div>

            <div class="small-12 columns">
                <div class="social-media-links UA_ShareModalLinks" style="text-align: left;">
                    <a href="mailto:?&amp;subject=From%20MDPI%3A%20%22A%20Privacy-Preserving%20and%20Attack-Aware%20AI%20Approach%20for%20High-Risk%20Healthcare%20Systems%20Under%20the%20EU%20AI%20Act&quot;&amp;body=https://www.mdpi.com/3247894%3A%0A%0AA%20Privacy-Preserving%20and%20Attack-Aware%20AI%20Approach%20for%20High-Risk%20Healthcare%20Systems%20Under%20the%20EU%20AI%20Act

Artificial%20intelligence%20%28AI%29%20has%20significantly%20driven%20advancement%20in%20the%20healthcare%20field%20by%20enabling%20the%20integration%20of%20highly%20advanced%20algorithms%20to%20improve%20diagnostics%2C%20patient%20surveillance%2C%20and%20treatment%20planning.%20Nonetheless%2C%20dependence%20on%20sensitive%20health%20data%20and%20automated%20decision-making%20exposes%20such%20systems%20to%20escalating%20risks%20of%20privacy%20breaches%20and%20is%20under%20rigorous%20regulatory%20oversight.%20In%20particular%2C%20the%20EU%20AI%20Act%20classifies%20AI%20uses%20pertaining%20to%20healthcare%20as%20%E2%80%9Chigh-risk%E2%80%9D%2C%20thus%20requiring%20the%20application%20of%20strict%20provisions%20related%20to%20transparency%2C%20safety%2C%20and%20privacy.%20This%20paper%20presents%20a%20comprehensive%20overview%20of%20the%20diverse%20privacy%20attacks%20that%20can%20target%20machine%20learning%20%28ML%29-based%20healthcare%20systems%2C%20including%20data-centric%20and%20model-centric%20attacks.%20We%20then%20propose%20a%20novel%20privacy-preserving%20architecture%20that%20integrates%20federated%20learning%20with%20secure%20computation%20protocols%20to%20minimally%20expose%20data%20while%20ensuring%20strong%20model%20performance.%20We%20outline%20an%20ongoing%20monitoring%20mechanism%20compliant%20with%20EU%20AI%20Act%20specifications%20and%20GDPR%20standards%20to%20further%20improve%20trust%20and%20compliance.%20We%20further%20elaborate%20on%20an%20independent%20adaptive%20algorithm%20that%20automatically%20tunes%20the%20level%20of%20cryptographic%20protection[...]" title="Email">
                        <i class="fa fa-envelope-square" style="font-size: 30px;"></i>
                    </a>

